guy%E1%BB%85n-Du/Tr%E1%BB%9F-binh-h%C3%A0nh/poem-wLBO_S7oDu5BwDnRbL0Axg">Trở binh hành - 阻兵行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C4%83n-Thi%C3%AAn-T%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/Tr%E1%BB%AB-d%E1%BA%A1/poem-Ar-lQWL0L9Ya7l_dIAP8Hw">Trừ dạ - 除夜</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C4%83n-Thi%C3%AAn-T%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/author-0ldtLxySSwRND3rGfSWz3g">Văn Thiên Tường</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%E1%BA%A1ch/T%E1%BB%AD-D%E1%BA%A1-xu%C3%A2n-ca/poem-CS0KPEgaZscoK-b-fxoyUA">Tử Dạ xuân ca - 子夜春歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%E1%BA%A1ch/author-evCCJA6g9JAScZSolcRfWA">Lý Thạch</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Th%C3%A1i/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-t%E1%BB%91-n%E1%BB%AF-%C4%91%E1%BB%93/poem-zKxXLoEGNYomPBDzqeOzqA">Vịnh tố nữ đồ - 詠素女圖</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Th%C3%A1i/author-Hcb43Ci-Tifm0ivlHzUJXg">Phạm Thái</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
